      "name": "Brass Lantern Guild",
      "public_front": "Maintains Gloamport’s gaslights, patrols fog-thick streets, and promotes public safety through orderly illumination.",
      "hidden_agenda": "Uses lantern-hums as a covert grid to locate, catalog, and lock down overlooked/impossible places before independent cartographers can reach them."
    },
    {
      "name": "Soot-Sweet Carnival Combine",
      "public_front": "A traveling fog-carnival offering joy, odd jobs, and reunions of the lost—for a price paid in coin, favors, or secrets.",
      "hidden_agenda": "Trades in nursery rhymes that bind shadows, sewing verses into clothing to control passageways and smuggle hidden doors between districts."
    },
    {
      "name": "Inkbone Archivists",
      "public_front": "Quiet binders and map-menders who restore damaged charts, sell ink, and keep civic records ‘for the common good.’",
      "hidden_agenda": "Collects and withholds missing atlas pages to assemble a ‘complete’ master map, erasing inconvenient wonders by overwriting them with false coordinates."
    }
  ]
}
```

